<item>
            <title>[FELIX-5775] Service properties not updated for lazy service when configuration changes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-5775</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If a lazy component is registered as a service, and this component is taking configurations, then the service properties are not updated if the component instance itself has not been instantiated yet.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
